OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FCold weather, icy conditions and
OL,8,Fspells of snow have created pressures
OL,9,Fin hospitals and difficulties for
OL,10,Fthose trying to travel in the region.
OL,12,FThe MET Office issued a yellow weather
OL,13,Fwarning for the south of Scotland on
OL,14,FTuesday January 6, while parts of
OL,15,FCumbria were issued a yellow snow and
OL,16,Fice warning in place until 11am on
OL,17,FTuesday.
