OL,7,FMost of England and Scotland has also
OL,8,Fbeen issued a yellow warning for 'icy
OL,9,Fpatches' between Tuesday night and
OL,10,FWednesday morning, which the
OL,11,Fforecaster says 'could lead to some
OL,12,Fdisruption.'
OL,14,FCarlisle saw a temperature of -7C in
OL,15,Fthe early hours of Tuesday morning,
OL,16,Fwhile Hawick and parts of southern
OL,17,FScotland plummeted further to -10C at
OL,18,Faround 3am.
