OL,7,FThe North Cumbria Integrated Care NHS
OL,8,FTrust said on Tuesday January 6 that
OL,9,Fit has seen "a huge increase in falls
OL,10,Fas a result of the icy weather," with
OL,11,F"almost triple the number of people
OL,12,Fwith fractured hips (neck of femur)
OL,13,Fover the past week compared to what we
OL,14,Fusually would expect."
