OL,7,FThe trust also said it has seen "other
OL,8,Ffalls-related injuries and people with
OL,9,Frespiratory issues flared up by the
OL,10,Fcold conditions," and it has urged
OL,11,Fpeople to "check on family members,
OL,12,Ffriends and neighbours who are elderly
OL,13,For frail".
OL,15,FAdding to the pressures, the Keswick
OL,16,FUrgent Treatment Centre closed on
OL,17,FTuesday due to staffing shortages.
