OL,7,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,8,Fhas issued amber cold-health alerts
OL,9,Ffor all regions of the UK until
OL,10,FSaturday January 11.
OL,12,FThe UKHSA anticipates that "forecast
OL,13,Fweather is expected to have
OL,14,Fsignificant impacts across health and
OL,15,Fsocial care services," including "a
OL,16,Frise in deaths, particularly among
OL,17,Fthose aged 65 and over".
