OL,7,FIn Scotland, despite continuing poor
OL,8,Fweather, all ScotRail tickets dated
OL,9,Fbetween January 2-5 can be used on
OL,10,Fservices running on Tuesday or
OL,11,FWednesday 6-7.
OL,13,FTuesday is the last day of engineering
OL,14,Fworks between Carlisle and Lockerbie,
OL,15,Fwith buses replacing this service.
