OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FTrain services between Carlisle and
OL,8,FNewcastle saw delays and cancellations
OL,9,Fon Tuesday, as a failed train between
OL,10,Fat Haltwhistle blocked some lines.
OL,11,FNorthern Rail anticipated delays of up
OL,12,Fto 45 minutes, while the 7.26 from
OL,13,FNewcastle to Carlisle, and the 9.53
OL,14,Fservice in the opposite direction were
OL,15,Fcancelled.
OL,17,FRail replacement bus services between
OL,18,FWhitehaven and Corkickle were
OL,19,Fsuspended for a few hours on Tuesday
OL,20,Fmorning due to the severe weather
OL,21,Fconditions.
