OL,7,FThe rail replacement service was
OL,8,Fstarted in in July 2025, after
OL,9,Fhistoric mine workings were discovered
OL,10,Fin the Bransty Tunnel when track
OL,11,Frenewal work began. Network Rail
OL,12,Fexpects the tunnel will not open until
OL,13,FSpring 2026.
OL,15,FHow have roads been affected?
OL,17,FIn Cumbria, a number of fell roads
OL,18,Fhave been closed due to icy conditions.
