OL,7,FCumbria Constabulary says that the
OL,8,FCold Fell and Corney Fell Roads are
OL,9,Fboth shut, as are the Hardknott Pass,
OL,10,Fthe Honister Pass, and the Newlands
OL,11,FPass.
OL,13,FSteel Brow near Frizington, a road to
OL,14,FWhitehaven, saw ice and snow on
OL,15,FTuesday morning which caused severe
OL,16,Fdelays for some travellers.
